item.title: Chriselda add a quote by Rainer Maria Rilke
item.description: "The necessary thing is after all but this; solitude, great inner solitude. Going into oneself for hours meeting no one - this one must be able to attain." -- Rainer Maria Rilke

item.title: Chriselda add a quote by Rainer Maria Rilke
item.description: "If you are patient in one moment of anger, you will escape a hundred days of sorrow" -- Rainer Maria Rilke

item.title: Chriselda add a quote by Rainer Maria Rilke
item.description: "There are no classes in life for beginners: right away you are always asked to deal with what is most difficult." -- Rainer Maria Rilke

item.title: Chriselda add a quote by Tupac Shakur
item.description: "You can spend minutes, hours, days, weeks, or even months over-analyzing a situation; trying to put the pieces together, justifying what could've, would've happened... or you can just leave the pieces on the floor and move the fuck on." -- Tupac Shakur

item.title: Chriselda add a quote by Lyndon B. Johnson
item.description: "Yesterday is not ours to recover, but tomorrow is ours to win or lose." -- Lyndon B. Johnson
